TEXT.S: Alex Blackwell Alex Blackwell sraral hya'ga sisyuw na NBA, wal malaxmisuq qaniy la. kawas tay 1970, ryax sa tay 27 nqu tay 6, Alex Blackwell, squliq na p'unro. Alex Blackwell hya ga wal malax senmong pgnaw mari na Amirika. pinqwasan nya' biru' Alex Blackwell hya ga minqwas biru' squ gaku' kya Monmouth College. pincyuwagan nya' pspngan mari sa may yugal yacing(1992 1993) plpgun ingalan nya' tinsu' minxal ga 1.3 teng. ru min 0.9 zmingat mari' na sinngusan naha'.
